snippet.title: Idol Showdown: Shishiro Botan Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Character Debut Trailer: Shishiro Botan / 獅白ぼたん

The Lioness drifts her way into Idol Showdown.
女ライオン、ドリフトしながらIdol Showdownに接近中！

Join the #IdolShowdown for FREE, coming Spring 2023.
